    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>本试玩版仅开放至剧情第1章。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280190/extras/7d8692eba3f7cc5169ba48dd31c49745.poster.avif?t=1770009640\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280190/extras/7d8692eba3f7cc5169ba48dd31c49745.webm?t=1770009640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280190/extras/7d8692eba3f7cc5169ba48dd31c49745.mp4?t=1770009640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为寻找世界上最美味的食物而踏上的旅程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在“料理”技术已消失已久的末日世界中，踏上寻找顶级美食的全新旅程。成为一名孤独的厨师，探索辽阔的世界，与魅力四射的同伴一同书写属于自己的独特故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280190/extras/f84e0a42353893cee8cc7312078e2995.poster.avif?t=1770009640\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280190/extras/f84e0a42353893cee8cc7312078e2995.webm?t=1770009640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280190/extras/f84e0a42353893cee8cc7312078e2995.mp4?t=1770009640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >将厨房用具用为武器，横屏平台动作游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白天和夜晚，随着时间变化出现各种敌人及首领。通过亲手制作的食物提升角色成长，或在冒险中遇到的同伴那里获得全新技能。利用一切手段击败敌人，并尝试获取特殊的料理食材。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280190/extras/6313e458a2eb61159780b5b95de65579.poster.avif?t=1770009640\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280190/extras/6313e458a2eb61159780b5b95de65579.webm?t=1770009640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280190/extras/6313e458a2eb61159780b5b95de65579.mp4?t=1770009640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >营地中展开的烈火盛宴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在艰辛的冒险之旅中，没有什么比食物更重要了。利用狩猎所获得的食材挑战各种山珍海味，或尝试制作意想不到的料理。在探索世界的过程中，可能会发现稀有的料理食谱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280190/extras/97722106fa5e917f39b9b8fd64de5845.poster.avif?t=1770009640\" width=700 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280190/extras/97722106fa5e917f39b9b8fd64de5845.webm?t=1770009640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280190/extras/97722106fa5e917f39b9b8fd64de5845.mp4?t=1770009640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >根据选择而变化的故事情节</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与充满魅力的人物，分享美好的故事。一同分享美食或进行多种对话，可快速建立友谊，也有可能恶化关系。大家的行动和对话选择将决定最终结果，因此可以享受丰富多彩的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
